  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith reveals second stage of Central Bank fraud",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa has said that the Pohottu government has put the country in a tragic situation and has turned the country into a refugee on a journey based on short-sightedness and illusion.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa today (25) stated that the only alternative to overcome this situation is a democratic, free and open people's struggle.",
        "He hoped that the present rulers would realize the true situation in the country and change their agenda in a way that would benefit the people, but that did not happen and they engaged in pagan politics and appointed a suitable gatekeeper for the people to enjoy for the next two years no matter what.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said that there was no point in a government that could not fulfill its promises to the people and protect the people.",
        "He also said that a large amount of money had been embezzled from gas as the second stage of the Central Bank fraud and that although the COPE committee had been exposed, all information had been withheld from the public.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said that an era of exploitation of even drugs and gas had been created, adding that there were gatekeepers who defended the Rajapaksas who rejected the country and opportunists who worked for narrow interests.",
        "The appointment of district representatives of the National Council of Intellectuals took place today (25). Accordingly, letters of appointment were handed over to the District Secretaries, Media Secretaries and other representatives representing the districts. The National Council of Intellectuals is an organization of university scholars and professionals affiliated to the Samagi Jana Balawegaya."
      ],
